# Advanced IAM Policies: Multiple Scenarios

## Overview

This document provides production-ready IAM policies for various S3 security scenarios, demonstrating the Principle of Least Privilege in different contexts.

---

## Scenario 1: Read-Only Application Access

**Use Case**: Web application needs to read static files from S3 (images, CSS, JS)

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowGetPublicAssets",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::company-assets-bucket/public/*",
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "aws:SourceVpc": "vpc-12345678"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowListBucketPublicPath",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::company-assets-bucket",
      "Condition": {
        "StringLike": {
          "s3:prefix": "public/*"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

---

## Scenario 2: Data Upload with Encryption Enforcement

**Use Case**: Backend application uploads processed data with mandatory encryption

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowPutObjectWithEncryption",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:PutObject",
        "s3:PutObjectAcl"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::secure-data-bucket/uploads/*/",
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "s3:x-amz-server-side-encryption": "aws:kms",
          "s3:x-amz-server-side-encryption-aws-kms-key-id": "arn:aws:kms:us-east-1:123456789012:key/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyUnencryptedUploads",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": "s3:PutObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::secure-data-bucket/uploads/*",
      "Condition": {
        "StringNotEquals": {
          "s3:x-amz-server-side-encryption": "aws:kms"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyIncorrectKMSKey",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": "s3:PutObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::secure-data-bucket/uploads/*",
      "Condition": {
        "StringNotLike": {
          "s3:x-amz-server-side-encryption-aws-kms-key-id": "arn:aws:kms:us-east-1:123456789012:key/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

