## Scenario 4: Time-Limited Access (for contractors/temporary staff)

**Use Case**: Contractor needs 30-day access to project files

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowTemporaryAccess",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:ListBucket"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::project-bucket",
        "arn:aws:s3:::project-bucket/project-xyz/*"
      ],
      "Condition": {
        "DateGreaterThan": {
          "aws:CurrentTime": "2026-04-13T00:00:00Z"
        },
        "DateLessThan": {
          "aws:CurrentTime": "2026-05-13T00:00:00Z"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

