## Scenario 5: Backup and Disaster Recovery Role

**Use Case**: Backup service can read all production data but cannot delete

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowReadAllBuckets",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListAllMyBuckets",
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:GetObjectVersion"
      ],
      "Resource": "*"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowBackupWrite",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:PutObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::backup-vault/*",
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "s3:x-amz-server-side-encryption": "AES256"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyDelete",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": [
        "s3:DeleteObject",
        "s3:DeleteObjectVersion",
        "s3:DeleteBucket",
        "s3:DeleteBucketPolicy"
      ],
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}
```

