## Scenario 6: Developer Sandbox (DEV only)

**Use Case**: DevOps engineer manages development buckets but NOT production

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowFullS3AccessDEVOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::dev-*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::dev-*/*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Sid": "DenyProductionAccess",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::prod-*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::prod-*/*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::production-*",
        "arn:aws:s3:::production-*/*"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

