## Scenario 8: Lambda Function (Serverless App)

**Use Case**: Lambda function processes images from S3 event notifications

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "AllowLambdaS3ReadOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::image-input-bucket/*"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowLambdaS3Write",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:PutObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::image-output-bucket/processed/*",
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "s3:x-amz-server-side-encryption": "AES256"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "AllowCloudWatchLogs",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "logs:CreateLogGroup",
        "logs:CreateLogStream",
        "logs:PutLogEvents"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:logs:*:*:*"
    }
  ]
}
```

